0.2.6:
  Bug Fix: The way some UI mods were handling caching was breaking building display. A compatibility fix has been implemented to fix this.
  Bug Fix: Fixed a minor issue where the "Deconstruct" button for roofs was not disabled under some circumstances.

0.2.4:
  Feature: Roofs are selectable! When the roof layer is enabled, select a roof tile to view its stats.
  Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where mechs (particularly constructoids) couldn't perform roof jobs.
  Bug Fix: Changed roofs to be displayed as buildable items rather than designators. This should help with compatibility with UI mods.
  Bug Fix: Slightly improved handling of roofs during gravship cutscenes when the roof layer is enabled.
  Bug Fix: Added support for migrating existing saved games.

0.1.2:
  Bug Fix: Create icons for roofs on the fly. This should greatly increase compatibility with mods that use custom menus.

0.1.1:
  Bug Fix: Removed unnecessary requirements for Odyssey on hull plating.

0.1.0:
  Feature: Many people have pointed out that thatch can actually be a very effective roofing material. A superior thatch roof is now available at the cost of hay, with primitive thatch remaining a free, basic construction option.
  Feature: Skylights are now tintable! After selecting a skylight to build, look for the "Set Glass Tint" button above the build panel.

0.0.16:
  Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where destroyed roofs could continue to be tracked behind the scenes.
  Bug Fix: Added full support for gravships, fixing a bug where gravship roofs would lose their stuff and hitpoints.
  Bug Fix: Changed the cost of reinforced glass to include a plasteel cost, fixing a problem where reinforced glass had the same cost as regular glass.
  Bug Fix: Lowered the stuff cost of luxury glass panels from 100 to 25, substantially reducing the cost.
  Bug Fix: Show skylight percentage without rounding.
  Bug Fix: Room stats weren't being marked as dirty after a room was built, resulting in stats lagging behind construction.
  Bug Fix: Updated Skyfaller roof impact logic to damage roofs in a radius, matching base game behavior.
  Bug Fix: Fixed a potential crash in SolarRoofMapComponent by ensuring PowerNet lookups occur on the main thread.
  Bug Fix: Added missing grid bounds checks in RoofIntegrityGrid to prevent IndexOutOfRangeException.
  Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where removing a roof would return base materials instead of the stuff it was built with.

0.0.6:
  Feature: Show roof hitpoints along with health percentage when damaged.
  Feature: Drop pod raids will attempt to find a nearby safe spot to land, so that drop pod raids remain relevant even with high-tier reinforced roofing. You should still expect drop pods to impact your roofs.
  Bug fix: Switched placeholder sound effect for thatch roof impacts.
  Bug fix: Corrected skyfaller impacts to properly impact against roofs.